void testSameDimOnTwoAxesFails(){
    assertQueryThrows("select {[Measures].[Unit Sales]} on columns,
" + " {[Measures].[Store Sales]} on rows
" + "from [Sales]", "Hierarchy '[Measures]' appears in more than one independent axis");
    assertQueryThrows("select {[Measures].[Unit Sales]} on columns,
" + " CrossJoin({[Product].members}," + "           {[Measures].[Store Sales]}) on rows
" + "from [Sales]", "Hierarchy '[Measures]' appears in more than one independent axis");
    assertQueryThrows("select CrossJoin(
" + "    {[Product].children},
" + "    {[Measures].[Unit Sales]}) on columns,
" + "    {([Product],
" + "      [Store].CurrentMember)} on rows
" + "from [Sales]", "Hierarchy '[Product]' appears in more than one independent axis");
    assertQueryThrows("select {[Measures].[Unit Sales]} on columns,
" + " {[Store].Members} on rows
" + "from [Sales]
" + "where ([Time].[1997].[Q1], [Measures].[Store Sales])", "Hierarchy '[Measures]' appears in more than one independent axis");
    executeQuery("with member [Measures].[West Coast Total] as " + " ' Aggregate({[Store].[USA].[CA], [Store].[USA].[OR], [Store].[USA].[WA]}) ' 
" + "select " + "   {[Measures].[Store Sales], 
" + "    [Measures].[Unit Sales]} on Columns,
" + " CrossJoin(
" + "   {[Product].children},
" + "   {[Store].children}) on Rows
" + "from [Sales]");
}
